dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4952f0e213ae6db8685b72f7e6bae2f4d8f71ee4","tid":1260933,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T05:56:52.000Z","msg":"又攪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原因：1.日子太急，2.集會已經好密要休息，3.太少人損士氣<br />\n<br />\n取消啦好嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:15:55.000Z","msg":"唔使取消<br />\n搞個網上直播算啦<br />\n畀人有多個選擇"},{"pid":"4a6682c9909ba9d16286ed3135d9cb76b2c9ac69","tid":1260933,"uid":261343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:24:06.000Z","msg":"曹文傑博士(小曹)於香港中文大學取得性別研究博士學位，研究興趣有性的現代性及酷兒理論。他活躍於本地同志及性權運動，現時擔任香港同志組織女同學社的執行幹事。&nbsp;<br />\n曹博士亦擔任《華人性權研究》副主編，此年度期刊由世界華人性學家協會出版。他也受香港特區政府委任為消除歧視性小眾諮詢小組成員。<br />\n<br />\n陳士齊博士，（Dr. CHAN Sze Chi，1957年－），人稱「齋 Sir」，香港宗教學者，經常議論時政，社會民主連線創辦人之一。曾任教香港浸會大學宗教及哲學系二十多年，是該校高級講師。<br />\n<br />\n許寶強說從來無感受到，有人因佔領而打壓他，更並非因此離開，只因大學不再是做教育的好地方：「你問和政治有無關？如果你將政治涵義放大，就一定有關。」他說的是整套教育制度，是校董委任制，也是一群文化研究學者，要坐下來開會討論學校開放日宣傳品上的Logo，究竟該如何設計的大學行政安排。<br />\n<br />\n我停了在一個地方，我想搞教育，但這種體制、考試安排、學術上生產方向，我覺得不合適自己興趣。<br />\n<br />\n許寶強突然離開嶺大文化研究系，是為了趕在60歲前，趁自己還有精力再出發。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nRespect!<br />\n真正的學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佩服您們的勇氣和承擔<br />\n一定支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56fad633c84bf5c2c4bde5835bc96c373c49a921","tid":1260933,"uid":26302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:27:43.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05df98354d8f7adf14facfac1feb8cc5e9bb668a","tid":1260933,"uid":36738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:29:29.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c70d6fdbf09a919b6d8adc4e6653732c852b07","tid":1260933,"uid":39698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:33:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c10058c69d7d2c8f5e2a12c69193971a60b89ce","tid":1260933,"uid":33153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:35:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"63122acbb001bd9f8bd598592e80376f71d88c07","tid":1260933,"uid":262863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T13:32:23.000Z","msg":"大力推！"},{"pid":"301b8c4dd2de8d105c19e6065a98d4b668fdad00","tid":1260933,"uid":257737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T14:04:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0de976726a03806387958f959e1631a73dbfb1b","tid":1260933,"uid":42627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T14:15:36.000Z","msg":"推!!!!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc5e62a96cf741770793e75d5bf5859456406b5","tid":1260933,"uid":21539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T14:17:12.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"8ad8e8d07e40070493756934c955af9cf17a227f","tid":1260933,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T14:17:44.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6592b6e94167daf9851fdecb85c928466fd437fd","tid":